Package Server.Controller

Class RMIGateway

java.lang.Object
java.rmi.server.RemoteObject
java.rmi.server.RemoteServer
java.rmi.server.UnicastRemoteObject
Server.Controller.RMIGateway
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Remote, RMIGatewayInterface
public class RMIGateway extends UnicastRemoteObject implements RMIGatewayInterface
The RMIGateway class represents the RMI gateway for the search engine system. It handles the communication between the client and the server.
